Introduction {#intro}
=====================

Issue: This document is an early draft. The shape of the API is still
being explored alongside the underlying [MoLE architecture
draft](https://github.com/Moderation-of-unLinkable-Endorsements/architecture-draft).

The Moderation of unLinkable Endorsements (MoLE) architecture allows a
user to carry trust signals across origins without becoming linkable
across those origins. This document describes the web-platform surface
through which web applications interact with that architecture.

Conformance {#conformance}
==========================

This specification follows the conformance and terminology conventions
of [[INFRA]] and [[!RFC2119]] / [[!RFC8174]].
